{"tid":1299339,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何韻詩於聯合國人權理事會發言　兩度被中方代表打斷","createTime":"2019-07-09T04:43:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T04:43:19.000Z","uid":163199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"44620f6be994359f5f72d9718fb5663d1744a9b1","tid":1299339,"uid":163199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:43:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1467335-20190709.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1467335-20190709.htm&d=R%2BBR62t8sBL7FL0rmd5Y1bidffPqrKRYdMEHu3E%2BQw4%3D&h=c0905e27\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1467335-20190709.htm&h=7c12806e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1467335-20190709.htm</a><br />\n歌手何韻詩到瑞士日內瓦出席聯合國人權理事會，並發表演說，講述在香港反對修訂《逃犯條例》的情況。<br />\n<br />\n何韻詩說，香港的民主及人權受到嚴重衝擊，「一國兩制」正步向死亡，要求聯合國將中國從人權理事會名單中剔除。<br />\n<br />\n中國代表在會上，兩度打斷何韻詩的發言，指她攻擊中國的「一國兩制」制度，以及使用侮辱性語言。"}]}